data.description:
1.64 acres with light covenants! This allows you to bring the animals, plenty of room to park the camper or other recreational toys. You will find a small greenhouse that will be perfect to start your gardening and then put the plants in the raised garden beds.
A large 33x33 shop allows plenty of room to park as well as have a nice work area. 
Step inside to 3 bedrooms with an additional room  (could be a non conforming bedroom/ no closet) that would make the perfect office or hobby room. Open bright floor plan. 
Enjoy the mountain views from the front deck and the comfort of knowing that you are minutes away from schools, golf courses, lakes, scratch gravel hiking trails, shopping and more.
